              In my experience the biggest net positive in the centralization of Gov IT is the inherent de-duping. The legacy stuff was rife with it. Not to mention incredibly poor security due to rank obligations. <br /><br />Full disclosure: I'm a contractor, I could be biased.

              

              
              
